Name: DOCKING
checklistText:
<size=21>DOCKING checklist</size>
Stabilize & align CSM
BMAG MODE (3) - ATT 1/RATE 2
At capture:
	PROBE EXTD/RETR tb-bp (A)
	CMC MODE - FREE
	Allow probe to damp S/C motions (approx 10 sec)
	DOCK PROBE RETRACT PRIM-1

After dock latches has engaged:
	PROBE EXTD/RETR tb - gray
	SECS PYRO ARM (2) - SAFE
	SECS LOGIC (2) - OFF
	EDS PWR - OFF
	cb EDS (3) - open
	DOCK PROBE EXTD/REL - OFF
	DOCK PROBE RETRACT (2) - OFF
	cb DOCK PROBE (2) - open
	PCM BIT RATE - LOW
